official_title: A bill to revise the boundaries of Olympic National Park and Olympic National Forest in the State of Washington, and for other purposes.

summary.text: (Measure passed Senate, amended) Modifies the boundaries of the Olympic National Park, the Olympic National Forest, and specified wilderness areas in Washington. Authorizes the Secretary of the Interior to acquire lands within the Park boundary. Authorizes appropriations.
